FBIS4-61016 "drsov085_t_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-085 Daily Report 2 May 1994 BALTIC STATES Estonia Tartu Party Official Urges Deportation of `Unwanted Aliens' Tartu Party Official Urges Deportation of `Unwanted Aliens' WS0205115994 Tallinn ETA in English 0810 GMT 2 May 94 WS0205115994 Tallinn ETA English BFN ["News Bulletin" No. 82/94] [Text] Estonian-Russian negotiations would escape from the present deadlock if Estonia approved an order of deportation of unwanted aliens, head of the National Independence Party Tartu section Andres Mae said. Russia would take Estonia more seriously if it demonstrated its willingness to maintain order, Mae said. But he admitted that the move would result in a major Russian propaganda offensive.
